text: So far, 6 mln or 63.56% of Hainanese have received one dose of #Covid19 #vaccine, with 1.22 mln fully vaccinated (two doses). #Hainan will get 1.5 mln more people the first dose in May while continuing to give the second doses, and achieve 75% #vaccination rate before late June. https://t.co/UNu6oENVmP
